  "prompt": "How can I completely eliminate sweaty palms?",
  "response": "Here are several strategies to reduce excessive hand sweating (hyperhidrosis):\n\n1. Medical treatments:\n- Prescription antiperspirants\n- Botox injections\n- Prescription oral medications\n- Iontophoresis (electrical treatment)\n- Anticholinergic medications\n\n2. Over-the-counter solutions:\n- Clinical strength antiperspirants\n- Glycopyrrolate-based hand lotions\n- Aluminum chloride products\n\n3. Natural remedies:\n- Sage tea or sage supplements\n- Apple cider vinegar\n- Black tea soaks\n- Avoid spicy foods and caffeine\n\n4. Lifestyle changes:\n- Manage stress through meditation/yoga\n- Keep hands cool and dry\n- Use talcum powder\n- Wear breathable gloves when appropriate\n\n5. Advanced treatments:\n- Microwave therapy\n- Surgical options like sympathectomy\n\n6. Daily management:\n- Carry hand towels\n- Use hand sanitizer with drying properties\n- Keep hands cool\n- Practice good hygiene\n\nIf sweating is severe and persistent, consult a dermatologist or healthcare professional for personalized treatment options.",
